data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION!!! NO HOA!! Metal roof and concrete block construction. Plenty of room for all your toys in the .27 acre enclosed yard!! This is not only one of the MOST AFFORDABLE homes in Central Merritt Island, but this oversized corner lot is situated between 3 local parks! You are a short walk or bike ride away down the newly poured sidewalks leading to Ulumay Wildlife Sanctuary where you can fish Sykes Creek, and a few minutes to both Kelly Park and Kiwanis Island Park to launch your boat, kayak, paddle board, or enjoy some of the amenities like tennis courts, playgrounds, picnic tables, soccer fields, and more! Watch rocket launches right from your back yard! Priced to reflect 2008 AC(coils in need of cleaning) and some cloth wiring. No repairs to be completed/priced as is due to the above. You won't find a better price for the location!
